{"tid":108784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]15歲女疑海邊拍照　遭大浪捲入海中亡","createTime":"2017-02-05T13:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T13:47:28.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d4a30d72965b795a8332609ff4c3968e98bdae","tid":108784,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:47:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170205/bkncn-20170205161225625-0205_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170205%2Fbkncn-20170205161225625-0205_05011_001.html&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQiwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=08ec3dfd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170205/bkncn-20170205161225625-0205_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170205/photo/bkncn-20170205161225625-0205_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170205%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170205161225625-0205_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=19139117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民昨晚於微博圖文並茂發貼稱，一名少女在廣東汕頭南澳田仔地質公園，疑因拍照時不幸跌落水，由於海浪太兇猛，無人救援，她在海上漂浮一個多小時，即使後來警員和救護人員到場，都只能在岸上無能無力。<br />\n<br />\n網上消息後來指出，一名來自湖南的李姓男子昨日偕家人到南澳田仔海邊遊玩，其間其15歲女兒站在海邊的岩石上看海，突然有一個大浪將其女兒捲入海中。由於當地海浪太大，他只能眼睜睜看着女兒被捲走。當日下午3時許，少女被打撈上岸，但已回天乏力，經搶救無效死亡。目前，具體死因仍在進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}